{"tid":697539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【梁天琦判囚】開埠以來最重, 比「六七暴動」更重","createTime":"2018-06-11T04:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T12:00:09.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0dcc36f6b39b0c2c669fc9b87c4255512822bc2c","tid":697539,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58303043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58303043&d=Vl0Luah8N1nyH6ezNtJ1EqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=fd1147ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58303043&h=89e16167\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58303043</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月11<br />\n<br />\n【梁天琦判囚】開埠以來最重 比六七暴動更重<br />\n<br />\n40,458<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0611 11:45<br />\n <br />\n本案為本港開埠以來暴動罪最重判刑，之前所有旺角騷亂案均只在裁判法院或區院審理，被控暴動罪的被告則在區院審理，在最先審理的幾宗案大致判監3年，有認罪的被告判監2年9個月，亦有因被告年輕，被判入教導所，判囚最重的被告同時涉及縱火，被判監4年9個月。<br />\n<br />\n但上月初一宗涉及11被告的暴動案，多名被告有掟磚，整體判刑較重，當中6人判囚逾3年半，最重判囚4年3個月。<br />\n<br />\n暴動罪在香港甚為罕見，過往僅曾用於六七暴動、白石難民營衝突及喜靈洲戒毒所騷亂事件。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>●六七暴動<br />\n<br />\n判刑：監禁兩年<br />\n1967年5月17日，被告嚴德偉（譯音）於南九龍裁判署外帶領一班暴動人士，嚴與另一人指警員正站在中國領土之上，他隨即轉身拍手，群眾拍手高呼和應，稍後更向警方投擲玻璃樽及石頭等雜物，嚴又鼓勵群眾襲擊警員，他本人更投擲汽油彈，事件歷時超過5小時。<br />\n三日後嚴在裁判署被判暴動罪成，監禁兩年，其後上訴，但遭駁回。</strong><br />\n<br />\n●白石船民中心暴動<br />\n<br />\n判刑：判囚9個月，但律政司申請加刑，最終改判5年。<br />\n1989年9月27日，20名越南船民手持木棍及鐵通自製的武器毆打其他敵對難民，最後演變成暴動，參與暴動人數多達100人。<br />\n<br />\n●喜靈洲戒毒所暴動<br />\n<br />\n判刑：被判囚3年，但律政司申請加刑，最終改判6年。<br />\n2000年6月4日，近200名喜靈洲本地囚犯圍堵越南囚犯倉，其後縱火及投擲起火物件，揚言要燒死越南人。"},{"pid":"2477e1a3b38f25e1c88a44fd7f8e020a1ac2171b","tid":697539,"uid":19527,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"楊光攞埋大紫荊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db4a17189749592819a83575ab7f311dfe42808","tid":697539,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">67班共狗就年年銷遙法外，清明拉大隊警犬仲幫手開路！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a1b24c7dab7def547bab8c57968615647c9e0e","tid":697539,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe584cfa027846154b84d55e5fe35b279ac9325","tid":697539,"uid":42767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"除左六七暴動唔同, 兩單暴動都係難民對難民/難民對囚友<br />\n<br />\n兩邊力量相等, 但今次暴動係武裝持盾警察對上暴動人士<br />\n<br />\n最終判刑比其他案件為高, 令香港市民摸不著頭腦"},{"pid":"97990e0077ded8389c4c9facf3441e01f0d93a24","tid":697539,"uid":171177,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c705ff7305f9014007731500ed421c8baadfeb4b","tid":697539,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"掟汽油彈都係兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93d8217e278160170b434f72a5fcced6b2e03d6","tid":697539,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97990e0077ded8389c4c9facf3441e01f0d93a24","tid":697539,"uid":171177,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"你想講咩?<br />\n<br />\n點解梁天琦判得重過67暴動?"},{"pid":"27